1
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:13,800
Is there something
troubling you, Quasimodo?

2
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:14,720
Oh, no!

3
00:00:15,040 --> 00:00:16,420
Oh, but there is.

4
00:00:17,420 --> 00:00:19,340
I know there is.

5
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:33,440
I think you're hiding something.

6
00:00:33,640 --> 00:00:34,640
Oh, no, Master.

7
00:00:34,920 --> 00:00:36,640
There's no... You're
not eating, boy.

8
00:00:38,160 --> 00:00:39,240
Very good.

9
00:00:39,900 --> 00:00:40,900
Thank you.

10
00:00:49,220 --> 00:00:50,220
Seeds.

11
00:00:51,470 --> 00:00:54,180
What's different in here?

12
00:00:54,680 --> 00:00:55,940
Nothing, sir.

13
00:00:58,400 --> 00:01:00,599
Isn't this one new?

14
00:01:00,620 --> 00:01:01,860
It's awfully good.

15
00:01:02,180 --> 00:01:04,720
Looks very much like the gypsy girl.

16
00:01:05,900 --> 00:01:06,900
I know.

17
00:01:07,260 --> 00:01:09,940
You helped her escape.

18
00:01:10,760 --> 00:01:15,580
But I... Now all Paris is
burning because of you.

19
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:17,860
She was kind to me, Master.

20
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,420
You idiots!

21
00:01:19,860 --> 00:01:21,040
That wasn't kindness.

22
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:21,880
It was cunning.

23
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:23,040
She's a gypsy.

24
00:01:23,041 --> 00:01:26,160
Gypsies are not capable of real love.

25
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:27,640
Think, boy.

26
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:29,360
Think of your mother.

27
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:37,171
But what chance could
a poor, misshapen child

28
00:01:37,183 --> 00:01:40,960
like you have against
her heathen treachery?

29
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:44,380
Well, never you mind, Quasimodo.

30
00:01:44,860 --> 00:01:46,820
She'll be out of our lives soon enough.

31
00:01:47,260 --> 00:01:50,080
I will free you from her evil spell.

32
00:01:50,081 --> 00:01:52,380
She will torment you no longer.

33
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,160
What do you mean?

34
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:57,900
I know where her hideout is.

35
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,280
And tomorrow at dawn,

36
00:02:00,140 --> 00:02:03,120
I attack with a thousand men.

